and his knees apart as

00:48:35.550 --> 00:48:36.610
if he were chafed.

00:48:36.610 --> 00:48:40.050
Rufus's father laughed,
and Rufus laughed, too.

00:48:40.050 --> 00:48:43.680
This time Charlie stole
