00:48:43.680 --> 00:48:45.430
What does that imply
about the audience?

00:48:45.430 --> 00:48:48.300
And intimate familiarity
with previous adventures

00:48:48.300 --> 00:48:51.790
of this character, an
ongoing routine connection.

00:48:54.300 --> 00:48:56.657
